Tidak mungkin!

00:10:08.859 --> 00:10:10.110
Pintu itu!

00:10:16.366 --> 00:10:17.617
Dia!

00:10:26.376 --> 00:10:27.377
Sedang apa kau?

00:10:27.627 --> 00:10:28.628
Pergi dari sini!

00:10:41.724 --> 00:10:43.936
Kau baik saja?

