Sekarang apa?

00:10:50.233 --> 00:10:51.484
Ini…

00:10:51.693 --> 00:10:52.735
…tidak baik.

00:11:26.686 --> 00:11:28.021
- [Peringatan gempa]
- Sial!

00:11:29.856 --> 00:11:30.898
Awas!

00:11:33.485 --> 00:11:35.070
Pergi dari sini!

00:11:45.998 --> 00:11:47.082
Sial…

00:11:48.791 --> 00:11:52.129
[Peringatan gempa]

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:06.601
Kenapa…

