00:17:17.870 --> 00:17:18.871
Kembali kemari!

00:17:19.914 --> 00:17:21.082
Sial!

00:17:29.799 --> 00:17:31.342
Apa…

00:17:31.718 --> 00:17:33.094
Ini tak mungkin terjadi!

00:17:37.348 --> 00:17:38.349
Tidak, tidak, tidak!

00:17:38.433 --> 00:17:39.333
Oh, Suzume.

00:17:39.434 --> 00:17:40.334
Tamaki!

00:17:40.393 --> 00:17:41.561
Maaf, aku keluar!

00:17:41.686 --> 00:17:43.104
Kau mau ke mana?

00:17:43.563 --> 00:17:46.023
Aku pulang cepat, mencemaskanmu.

00:17:46.148 --> 00:17:47.049
Karena gempa?

00:17:47.108 --> 00:17:48.610
Kau tak mengangkat teleponmu.

00:17:48.735 --> 00:17:50.027
Maaf! Aku tak dengar.

00:17:50.152 --> 00:17:50.945
Tapi aku baik-baik saja.

00:17:51.070 --> 00:17:52.113
H… Hei…

00:17:52.238 --> 00:17:54.491
Suzume! Jawab aku!

00:17:57.744 --> 00:17:58.995
Hei, anak kucing!

00:18:09.964 --> 00:18:11.132
Apa itu?

00:18:11.257 --> 00:18:12.467
Permisi!

00:18:14.218 --> 00:18:16.763
Apa yang sedang terjadi?

00:18:25.605 --> 00:18:28.441
Hei, Suzume!

00:18:29.358 --> 00:18:30.610
Hei!

00:18:30.943 --> 00:18:31.944
Mau…

00:18:31.986 --> 00:18:33.279
…ke mana?

00:18:33.821 --> 00:18:35.114
Apa…

00:18:40.119 --> 00:18:41.621
Ah!

00:18:42.497 --> 00:18:44.916
Maaf!

00:18:46.959 --> 00:18:49.211
Terima kasih atas kesabaran Anda.

