[POST TERUNGGAH]

00:24:33.597 --> 00:24:35.224
Ini khas dia, 'kan?

00:24:35.349 --> 00:24:36.350
Bagaimana bisa…

00:24:36.392 --> 00:24:36.976
[LIHAT SIAPA YANG KUTEMUI]

00:24:37.184 --> 00:24:38.185
