00:36:26.852 --> 00:36:28.103
Uhhh...

00:36:28.228 --> 00:36:29.395
Bukankah itu hebat?

00:36:31.106 --> 00:36:33.233
Hei, Souta!

00:36:34.192 --> 00:36:37.112
Bangunlah!

00:36:38.654 --> 00:36:39.906
Ugh.

